1. *Dečka* je često viđen u parku. (The boy is often seen in the park.)
2. Ona je izabrala *dečka* iz grupe. (She chose the boy from the group.)
3. Njen *dečka* joj je dao poklon. (Her boyfriend gave her a gift.)
4. Ona se zaljubila u *dečka* iz susedstva. (She fell in love with the boy from the neighborhood.)
5. Njegov *dečka* mu je dao najbolju podršku. (His boyfriend gave him the best support.)